    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/moore-speaks-bsg-backstory-and-fracks-it#comment-6722" class="active">But why don&#039;t you get upset</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by Henrik (not verified) on Tue, 2009-01-20 01:42.</div>
